description: The video shows an animated, stylized image of a woman holding a heart-shaped box of chocolates. The woman has light blond hair styled in a retro fashion and bright blue eyes. She's wearing a light green dress with short, puffed sleeves. She has fair skin and red lipstick. She holds the red heart-shaped box in front of her with both hands which she then shakes and holds to her ear. A yellow ribbon is tied around the box in a bow. A small sparkle appears on the surface of the box of chocolates in the center.
